reviews.text: German restaurant serving draft beer, decor is very nice, this time staff were not enough in the floor area, couldn’t give a good service, the food is good, must try the pork knuckle and their sausages. Prices are fair for this type of food, and their set(lunch, dinner) are in a very good price. They have a wide drinks menu, wine, beer, cocktails, mocktails.
Only good thing is the happy hour for drinks from 3pm to 8pm
Nice decor and atmosphere plus friendly staff. Really lovely food and drink.  Just what we needed. Definitely will be back.

Very yummy German bar restaurant. Food has good portions and taste good. Staff is very friendly. During happy hours, you got discount on beers, till 8pm I think. Will definitely go again. Good place for group gatherings.
Great place for beer

reviews.text: Vast selection of baby related merchandise, Parents favorite. A huge supermarket sits next to this department store as well. A true one stop shop for families
Huge mall, connected to other shopping as well.  Good transportation options in and out.
Great place for shopping, especially for beauty products! Family mall with everything you need.

Central location. Linked to 5 or 6 other shopping arcades. Linked to the subway line at Tuen Mun station. Many car parks, and some offer free parking with purchase. I'm happy with this place as I'm always able to find whatever I'm looking for here. Finding my car after getting parking ticket stamped is always a challenge tho.
This is the closest to home and what you get.ftom.anywhere, you get it here  mostly, why ho anywhere else. My kids are practical, when they are here, they love it just here.

reviews.text:
閒日，午餐時間約12點。
雖然客人不多，約有8枱客人，但只有1位客服，實在不夠。
情況約在12點半後因有其他客服上班而得到改善。
食物味道和價格可以接受。
豬手唔够香脆 德國腸非常咸 青口還有冰 食物質數非常差 招呼也不好 不會再去

German restaurant serving draft beer, decor is very nice, this time staff were not enough in the floor area, couldn’t give a good service, the food is good, must try the pork knuckle and their sausages. Prices are fair for this type of food, and their set(lunch, dinner) are in a very good price. They have a wide drinks menu, wine, beer, cocktails, mocktails.
1個人食飽要200元 味道OK  未試過 豬手好唔好食 唔夠代表性
等位幾快，午餐75折，88至168一個，再加一，份量足。座位闊落。
